      "parameters": {
        "width": 320,
        "height": 560,
        "content": "## üõ†Ô∏è Background Removal MCP Server ‚úÖ 3 operations\n\n### About\nRemove the background of any image\n\n### üîß How it Works\n\nThis workflow converts the Background Removal API into an MCP-compatible interface for AI agents.\n\n‚Ä¢ **MCP Trigger**: Serves as your server endpoint for AI agent requests\n‚Ä¢ **HTTP Request Nodes**: Handle API calls to https://api.remove.bg/v1.0\n‚Ä¢ **AI Expressions**: Automatically populate parameters via `$fromAI()` placeholders\n‚Ä¢ **Native Integration**: Returns responses directly to the AI agent\n"
